    "# Task 4: Visualizing Standardized Data with Seaborn"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "Text(0.5, 1.0, 'Violinplot for diagnosis')"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 8,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 720x720 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "data = x\n",
    "data_std = (data - data.mean()) / data.std()\n",
    "data = pd.concat([y, data_std.iloc[:,0:10]], axis=1)\n",
    "data = pd.melt(data,id_vars='diagnosis',var_name='features',value_name='value')\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(10,10))\n",
    "sns.violinplot(x='features',y='value',hue='diagnosis',data=data,split=True,inner='quart')\n",
    "plt.xticks(rotation=45);\n",
    "plt.title('Violinplot for diagnosis',size=30)"
   ]
  },
